query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, COUNT(p.id) as pet_count 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN pets p ON p.user_id = u.id 
GROUP BY u.id, u.name, u.email 
ORDER BY u.id DESC 
LIMIT 10;
